courses
  course_id ref_num

  When an instructor requests to opt-out
    Add the user to the list

  Once the user is added to the list
    Add the course id that they are opting out
    If any sections, then add sections

Once the user has passed the CM course
  Toggle the passed option
  Toggle Role to Faculty from Faculty-VCF (VCF)

Set role to Faculty (F) (Toggle):
  Collect the course and sections for the user
  create a connection to the api
  update the role to the sections to: F
